node.text: I get asked a lot about my emotions after a loss and how I keep smiling through all that life has thrown at me….. well the truth is, it’s not always sunshine and rainbows. Rocky said it best “life is about how hard you can get hit and keep moving forward”. I took this loss and every loss extremely hard. I can honestly say that I worked my ass off and put 100% of myself in that fight. I want to be someone that others can look at and say, one loss does not define me. I am so much more then what I do for a living. I am going to continue fighting because that is what I do. I am a strong, beautiful, talented women. I do not quit when things get hard, I quit when I am finished. And I am not finished!! Thank you for all the support from my fans. This video is for you.  Link in bio.

Try all you want, there's no putting me in a box or defining me as one thing.  I #LevelUp every day I decide to attack something new, with the passion and determination necessary to win it all.  I'm uncompromising in my commitment to excelling at everything, and that includes finding the perfect condom that actually makes sex more fun and enjoyable.  Find your perfect fit and feel that maximizes confidence and swagger with @trojancondoms #UltraFit, we certainly did #Ad. 

*

*

#TrojanULTRAFIT condoms are available exclusively at Walmart and if you buy in-store, you can enter the #UltraFitSweepstakes running from June 15- August 31 with weekly drawings to win big prizes that will level up your lifestyle. Hit the link in bio for details.

*

*

NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. Void where prohibited. Open to legal residents of the U.S. and D.C. 18 years or older and age of majority. Begins 06/15/2021 at 12:00:01 a.m. ET and ends on 08/31/21 at 11:59:59 p.m. ET. Prize/Odds: Total ARV of all Prizes up to $59,223.50. Odds of winning depend on the total number of eligible entries received. For Official Rules, complete details and how to enter without making a purchase, visit Rules.TrojanUltraFitSweeps.com. Sponsor: Church & Dwight, Co., Inc., Princeton South Corporate Center, 500 Charles Ewing Blvd., Ewing, NJ 08628
